data.description: Large four bedroom home in a wonderful, quiet, gated community with the best neighbors anyone can ask for! The house is very quiet inside and very cool with the large amount of tile covering the majority of the floor.  Appliances are the best and all Whirlpool except for the washer and dryer which are frigidaire.  All appliances come with the house and are fully paid for.  The appliances were NOT purchased with the house, they were purchased separately by the owner.
data.whatILove: Peaceful and quiet neighborhood!  Excellent neighbors!  Watching the squirrels in the backyard during the day and at night you can see the Opossums and Raccoons looking for a bite to eat.  You may also see the Wily Fox as he comes through the backyard since the Nature  Preserve is directly behind the house so....no houses behind me!  If you have a dog or two this is the perfect place to walk your dog and let him or her meet the neighbors dogs.  You won't be disappointed if you lived here!  You would love it and know you made the right decision moving in.
